        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>You strategically craft your debilitations to lessen or negate an enemy's tactical advantages. Add the following debilitations to the list you can choose from when you use @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Debilitating Strike]{Debilitating Strike}.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Debilitation</strong> The target can't flank other creatures, and it can't provide flanking for its allies.</li>\n<li><strong>Debilitation</strong> The target doesn't gain a circumstance bonus to AC from @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Raise a Shield]{Raising a Shield}, lesser cover, or standard cover; it gains only a +2 circumstance bonus to AC from greater cover or @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Take Cover]{Taking Cover}.</li>\n</ul>"
